  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The sky half of the Full Column — designed explicitly for coupling with OCEANDEEP's Full Column Low. HP filter at 200 Hz removes all ground reference, leaving the upper register entirely to OPENSKY. Shimmer at hall level (0.55 feedback). No sub — OCEANDEEP provides the abyss. Wide stereo spread. The Full Column Principle: flying fish do not compete with anglerfish; they share the column. Each engine occupies its stratum. Together: the entire mythology.",
  "tags": [
    "opensky",
    "coupling",
